text: "I'm Good (Blue)" is a 2022 song by French DJ David Guetta and American singer Bebe Rexha. The song samples the 1998 song "Blue (Da Ba Dee)" by Italian group Eiffel 65. It topped the single charts in Australia, Austria, Belgium, Canada, the Czech Republic, Denmark, Finland, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Iceland, Latvia, Luxembourg, the Netherlands, Norway, Poland, Romania, Slovakia, Sweden, Switzerland and the United Kingdom. It was nominated for an Grammy Award in 2023. == References == Category:2022 songs Category:David Guetta songs
